              To better cope with stress, uncertainty and challenges, neuroscience research increasingly points to the concept of brain fitness.

         </div>
        </section>

            </h5>

            <div class="_3XK8N">
             <h5 class="_2EuJH" data-pb-type="lb">
              Exclusive
             </h5>
             <h5 class="_1XJ15" data-pb-type="tg">
              <a href="/topic/australia-votes-1lyo">
               Australia votes
              </a>
             </h5>
            </div>
            <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
             <a data-testid="article-link" href="/politics/federal/greens-election-strategy-bets-on-australians-embracing-hung-parliament-20210321-p57clv.html">
              Greens election strategy bets on Australians embracing hung Parliament
             </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
             Greens leader Adam Bandt will name nine target seats for the party in a bid to gain the balance of power, calculating this is far more likely than an outright Labor victory on polling.
            </p>

       <section class="_3U0Iv cMu-d _2p1IG _3sK3r" data-an-name="Drive" data-contentunit-id="18" data-pb-type="cu" data-testid="drive-strap">
        <header class="iBWLf">
         <h2 class="_3iLAo" data-pb-type="hi">
          <a href="http://www.drive.com.au" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
           Cars by
           <span class="wUELX">
            drive
           </span>
          </a>
         </h2>
        </header>
        <div class="_19wF2">
         <div class="_15r1L gts1Q _1pUSK" data-an-position="1" data-pb-type="st" data-testid="story-tile">
          <figure class="XmCQH" data-pb-type="im">
           <a data-testid="article-link" href="https://www.drive.com.au/news/subaru-wilderness-off-road-line-to-launch-this-month-to-target-jeep-and-bronco-125289.html?trackLink=SMH1" rel="noopener noreferrer" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">
            <div class="_1hWPs _2f0dW J7Q0t _2mu0j">

           <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/afl/four-points-why-this-was-the-opening-round-we-and-the-afl-needed-20210321-p57clr.html">

            </a>
           </h3>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            An excellent suite of matches and a feeling that the game was back to where it had been when at its best.
           </p>
           <div class="_8SnR- _1vuby _3WqBN" data-pb-type="au">
            <h5 class="_2DPTm">
             <span>
              <span>
               <a href="/by/michael-gleeson-hveeu" title="Articles by Michael Gleeson">
                Michael Gleeson
               </a>
              </span>
             </span>
            </h5>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="_15r1L KrNcv _3R9_F" data-an-position="7" data-contentunit-parent-id="20" data-pb-type="st" data-testid="story-tile">
          <figure class="XmCQH" data-pb-type="im">
           <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/soccer/struggling-a-league-team-shouts-the-bar-after-match-rained-out-20210321-p57coc.html" tabindex="-1">
            <div class="_1hWPs _2f0dW J7Q0t _2mu0j">
             <picture class="">
              <source data-pb-im-config='{"aspectRatio":1.5,"type":"landscape3x2","width":267}' media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcset="https://static.ffx.io/images/$zoom_0.3047%2C$multiply_0.3532%2C$ratio_1.5%2C$width_756%2C$x_386%2C$y_72/t_crop_custom/q_86%2Cf_auto/070aca578098bf6a5affa4b2b369ab67f30ae186, https://static.ffx.io/images/$zoom_0.3047%2C$multiply_0.7063%2C$ratio_1.5%2C$width_756%2C$x_386%2C$y_72/t_crop_custom/q_62%2Cf_auto/070aca578098bf6a5affa4b2b369ab67f30ae186 2x"/>

             </picture>
            </div>
           </a>
          </figure>
          <div class="_1YzQk _24ZSP">
           <div class="_3XK8N">
            <h5 class="_1XJ15" data-pb-type="tg">
             <a href="/topic/melbourne-victory-5tt">
              Melbourne Victory
             </a>
            </h5>
           </div>
           <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/soccer/struggling-a-league-team-shouts-the-bar-after-match-rained-out-20210321-p57coc.html">
             Struggling A-League team shouts the bar after match rained out
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            Melbourne Victory cant take a trick on the pitch but club bosses know one way to appease frustrated fans.
           </p>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
